OL,3,CJustice Secretary calls on MSPs to
OL,4,Cunite against winter fuel payment cut
OL,6,FThe UK Labour Government's "abrupt
OL,7,Fdecision" to bring in means-testing
OL,8,Ffor the winter fuel payment has
OL,9,F"robbed millions of pensioners",
OL,10,FScotland's social justice secretary
OL,11,Fhas said.
OL,13,FSpeaking ahead of a parliamentary
OL,14,Fdebate later on Tuesday, Shirley-Anne
OL,15,FSomerville has called on MSPs to unite
OL,16,Fagainst the UK Government's decision
OL,17,Fand restore the Winter Fuel Payment to
OL,18,Fall of the appropriate age.
