OL,3,CJustice Secretary calls on MSPs to
OL,4,Cunite against winter fuel payment cut
OL,6,FShe said: "Labour's abrupt decision to
OL,7,Fbring in means-testing for the winter
OL,8,Ffuel payment has robbed millions of
OL,9,Fpensioners of hundreds of pounds at
OL,10,Fthe very time that energy bills are
OL,11,Fset to rise by an average of #150 a
OL,12,Fyear.
OL,14,F"Today in parliament, as we mark
OL,15,FChallenge Poverty Week, I call on MSPs
OL,16,Ffrom across the chamber to unite and
OL,17,Fdemand that the UK Government reverse
OL,18,Fthis callous decision and restore the
OL,19,FWinter Fuel Payment to all our
OL,20,Fpensioners.
OL,26,@nD@KOUvD@AOU
