OL,3,CJustice Secretary calls on MSPs to
OL,4,Cunite against winter fuel payment cut
OL,6,F"As we head toward what will be
OL,7,Fanother difficult winter for many
OL,8,Fpensioners, this is less of a party
OL,9,Fpolitical issue and more a national
OL,10,Fpriority.
OL,12,F"Over in Ireland, they are talking
OL,13,Fabout extending their winter fuel
OL,14,Fpayment for pensioners ` but here in
OL,15,Fthe UK, older people are being forced
OL,16,Fto pay the price for Westminster's
OL,17,Feconomic incompetence."
